WEBVTT

1
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:19,843
Ooh.

2
00:00:27,984 --> 00:00:29,259
Woi, berhenti, berhenti!

3
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:34,693
Illumination!

4
00:01:58,910 --> 00:02:00,977
Waktunya tidur.

5
00:02:00,978 --> 00:02:03,045
Woo-hoo, tidur!

6
00:02:03,046 --> 00:02:04,519
Mantap!

7
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,289
Yah, jangan dong.

8
00:02:05,290 --> 00:02:07,950
Bobo, bobo, bobo!

9
00:02:08,458 --> 00:02:10,492
Udah cuci muka belum?

10
00:02:10,493 --> 00:02:12,296
Udah.

11
00:02:12,297 --> 00:02:13,462
Mm... belum sih.

12
00:02:16,565 --> 00:02:18,467
Dongeng dulu! Dongeng dulu!

13
00:02:20,173 --> 00:02:22,339
Woo-hoo!

14
00:02:22,340 --> 00:02:25,276
Ssst. Ssst.

15
00:02:28,973 --> 00:02:30,281
"Zaman dulu kala,

16
00:02:30,282 --> 00:02:34,978
"ada putri pemberani dan baik hati
bernama Peach.

17
00:02:34,979 --> 00:02:38,817
"Dia adalah pelindung hebat
Kerajaan Jamur.

18
00:02:38,818 --> 00:02:41,292
Ceritanya dimulai
bertahun-tahun yang lalu..."

19
00:02:41,293 --> 00:02:43,954
Mau dengar cerita
tentang tukang ledengnya!

20
00:02:43,955 --> 00:02:46,660
- Ooh, ooh.
- Itu kan sudah kemarin malam,

21
00:02:46,661 --> 00:02:49,201
malam sebelumnya,
dan malamnya lagi juga itu terus.

22
00:02:49,202 --> 00:02:50,862
Tukang ledeng, tukang ledeng.

23
00:02:50,863 --> 00:02:54,965
- Ledeng, ledeng, ledeng!
- Tukang ledeng.

24
00:02:54,966 --> 00:02:56,065
- Tukang ledeng.
- Oke, oke.

25
00:02:56,066 --> 00:02:59,508
Woo-hoo!
Gue emang ngefans sama si kembar itu.

26
00:03:00,543 --> 00:03:02,214
"Mario dan Luigi dulu..."

27
00:03:02,215 --> 00:03:04,612
- Langsung ke bagian Donkey Kong dong.
- Oh, oh.

28
00:03:04,613 --> 00:03:08,880
Donkey Kong,
Donkey Kong, Donkey Kong,

29
00:03:08,881 --> 00:03:10,618
Donkey Kong, Donkey Kong,

30
00:03:10,619 --> 00:03:12,917
Donkey...

31
00:03:17,824 --> 00:03:19,858
Sisanya kita lanjut besok ya.

32
00:03:19,859 --> 00:03:21,123
- Yah.
- Gak seru ah.

33
00:03:21,124 --> 00:03:23,433
Sana masuk selimut,
tidur ya?

34
00:03:23,434 --> 00:03:25,093
Huuu.

35
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:30,340
Bentar ya, aku balik lagi.

36
00:03:46,754 --> 00:03:49,459
Putri Rosalina,

37
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:52,231
ikut gue sekarang.

38
00:04:44,449 --> 00:04:46,516
Lo cari gara-gara sama...

39
00:04:46,517 --> 00:04:48,452
Mama?

40
00:04:48,453 --> 00:04:51,047
Aku mimpi buruk.

41
00:04:51,247 --> 00:04:54,688
Waduh. Itu bukan mimpi, sayang.

42
00:05:08,308 --> 00:05:10,572
Ha...?

43
00:05:34,257 --> 00:05:39,602
Dari sisa-sisa kekalahan bokapnya,
lahirlah penakluk baru.

44
00:05:39,603 --> 00:05:43,969
Nama Bowser bakalan ditakuti
sekali lagi!

45
00:05:46,005 --> 00:05:47,445
Bisa diam gak sih?

46
00:05:46,446 --> 00:05:49,876
Gue cuma seneng banget buat lo.

47
00:05:49,877 --> 00:05:52,813
Penculikan putri pertama lo!

48
00:05:54,618 --> 00:05:56,618
Jangan gangguin mama gue!

49
00:05:56,983 --> 00:05:58,819
Jangan!

50
00:06:42,127 --> 00:06:43,996
Hah?

51
00:06:50,971 --> 00:06:53,367
Wahoo!

52
00:07:16,469 --> 00:07:18,436
Woo-hoo!

53
00:07:25,841 --> 00:07:28,809
Woo-hoo!

54
00:07:45,124 --> 00:07:46,564
Hei, hah?

55
00:07:46,565 --> 00:07:49,259
Lu, lompatan lo yang tadi itu...

56
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:52,427
Mario, kita sekarang jadi
anak motor keren ya?

57
00:07:52,428 --> 00:07:53,230
Ya jelaslah.

58
00:07:53,231 --> 00:07:55,474
- Oh, kalian udah di sini.
- Oh.

59
00:07:55,475 --> 00:07:58,070
Terus, pipa mana yang bermasalah?

60
00:08:01,481 --> 00:08:03,240
Oke, oke.

61
00:08:03,241 --> 00:08:04,945
Tunjuk aja deh?

62
00:09:14,147 --> 00:09:18,447
Oke, kayaknya kita ikutin aja
suara serem itu.

63
00:09:26,489 --> 00:09:27,324
Ayo dong.

64
00:09:27,325 --> 00:09:29,293
Lo kan bukan
si penakut lagi.

65
00:09:30,163 --> 00:09:33,098
Masih kok! Orang tuh gak berubah!

66
00:09:50,315 --> 00:09:53,448
Itu dia masalahnya.

67
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:01,126
Ooh.

68
00:10:06,606 --> 00:10:08,332
Balikin batanya. Balikin!

69
00:10:08,333 --> 00:10:11,775
Gue ngelihat ke lubang itu,
dan setannya ngelihat balik.

70
00:10:29,354 --> 00:10:32,422
Hei. Gak apa-apa kok.

71
00:10:41,135 --> 00:10:43,465
Pelan-pelan.

72
00:10:49,572 --> 00:10:51,782
- Ah.
- Hei, oke.

73
00:10:51,783 --> 00:10:53,278
Oke, tenang ya.

74
00:10:53,279 --> 00:10:55,181
Nama lo siapa, mahluk kecil?

75
00:10:55,182 --> 00:10:56,446
Yoshi.

76
00:10:56,447 --> 00:10:57,887
Salam kenal, Yoshi.

77
00:10:56,888 --> 00:10:59,384
Gimana ceritanya lo bisa masuk pipa?

78
00:11:00,385 --> 00:11:01,352
Oh...

79
00:11:25,278 --> 00:11:27,949
Awas, minggir dari jalanan!

80
00:11:40,161 --> 00:11:43,360
Ada monyet tahun 81 nih...

81
00:11:48,334 --> 00:11:51,401
Mm? Apa...? Oh!

82
00:12:15,758 --> 00:12:17,990
Ya sudahlah, kita gak bakal tahu.

83
00:12:13,997 --> 00:12:16,031
- Masalahnya ketemu.
- Ah.

84
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:25,403
- Halo, Yoshi.
- Yoshi.

85
00:12:25,404 --> 00:12:27,141
Yoshi. Yoshi.

86
00:12:27,142 --> 00:12:29,880
Yoshi. Yoshi.

87
00:12:29,881 --> 00:12:32,179
Ribet amat cuma gara-gara Yoshi.

88
00:12:32,180 --> 00:12:36,677
Iya. Tadi kita nemu
anak kecil ini dan...

89
00:12:37,185 --> 00:12:39,713
Lah, ke mana dia?

90
00:12:40,122 --> 00:12:41,353
Hah.

91
00:12:41,354 --> 00:12:43,388
Yaudah, dia kelihatan baik kok.

92
00:12:46,964 --> 00:12:49,262
Rrr, rrr.

93
00:12:49,263 --> 00:12:52,397
Dia tahu kan itu motor gue?

94
00:13:33,274 --> 00:13:35,979
Kalian mau bawa kita ke mana?

95
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:38,014
Nikmati aja, Tuan Putri.

96
00:13:38,015 --> 00:13:43,513
Ini tempat terakhir
yang bakal lo lihat selagi hidup.

97
00:14:38,174 --> 00:14:39,768
Keren banget kan?

98
00:14:39,769 --> 00:14:42,979
Gue rasa bokap bakalan
suka banget.

99
00:14:46,182 --> 00:14:48,315
Mama, aku takut.

100
00:14:48,316 --> 00:14:50,778
Bakalan baik-baik aja kok.

101
00:15:04,266 --> 00:15:05,563
Pasukan Koopa-ku,

102
00:15:05,564 --> 00:15:07,796
tebak siapa yang nyulik putri.

103
00:15:07,797 --> 00:15:09,435
Ah...

104
00:15:09,436 --> 00:15:11,338
Dan bukan sembarang putri.

105
00:15:11,339 --> 00:15:15,540
Pelindung kosmos,
ibunda dari para bintang.

106
00:15:15,541 --> 00:15:19,918
Dengan kekuatannya,
kita bakal hancurin alam semesta!

107
00:15:19,919 --> 00:15:23,647
Dia bakal korbankan nyawanya
demi kejayaan kita!

108
00:15:24,517 --> 00:15:26,584
Gimana pidato gue tadi?

109
00:15:26,585 --> 00:15:29,454
Sangat deskriptif.

110
00:15:32,492 --> 00:15:34,262
Aduh! Aduh!

111
00:15:35,066 --> 00:15:39,200
Gak ada yang boleh sakitin anak gue.

112
00:15:43,635 --> 00:15:45,471
Pergi!

113
00:16:04,590 --> 00:16:08,296
Pertempuran besar
dalam hidup gue sudah dekat.

114
00:16:07,297 --> 00:16:12,794
Waktunya buat bebasin bokap gue.

115
00:16:35,885 --> 00:16:36,995
Kira-kira dia bakal suka gak ya?

116
00:16:36,996 --> 00:16:41,461
Mario, lo naksir ya
sama si putri?

117
00:16:41,462 --> 00:16:42,693
Apa?!

118
00:16:41,694 --> 00:16:44,629
Lah, apa salahnya kalau cowok
ngasih kado spesial

119
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:49,106
buat sahabatnya sendiri,
buat nunjukin betapa berartinya dia?

120
00:16:49,107 --> 00:16:53,407
♪ Pas rembulan kena mata lo ♪

121
00:16:53,408 --> 00:16:55,211
♪ Kayak pizza yang gede banget ♪

122
00:16:55,212 --> 00:16:58,313
- ♪ Itu lah... ♪
- ♪ A-Yoshi. ♪

123
00:16:58,314 --> 00:17:00,612
Gue gak jatuh cinta sama Peach kok.

124
00:17:00,613 --> 00:17:02,515
Mwah, mwah.

125
00:17:02,516 --> 00:17:05,386
Udah ah, cabut yuk.

126
00:17:12,064 --> 00:17:13,196
♪ Yeah, yeah ♪

127
00:17:13,197 --> 00:17:16,529
- ♪ Hey, hey ♪
- Bilang "mushroom."

128
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:19,301
♪ Yeah... ♪

129
00:17:19,302 --> 00:17:21,269
Ooh.

130
00:17:25,803 --> 00:17:27,342
Mmm.

131
00:17:27,343 --> 00:17:28,805
Halo, teman-teman.

132
00:17:27,806 --> 00:17:29,707
Halo, Toad.

133
00:17:29,708 --> 00:17:32,379
Keren juga gaya lo.

134
00:17:32,942 --> 00:17:35,086
Hm, siapa nih?

135
00:17:35,087 --> 00:17:37,352
Yoshi.

136
00:17:37,353 --> 00:17:40,784
- Siapa sih yang bisa nolak muka lucu gini?
- Aw...

137
00:17:42,490 --> 00:17:43,820
Ayo.

138
00:17:43,821 --> 00:17:46,130
Jadi tiba-tiba ada dinosaurus keren
muncul gitu aja

139
00:17:46,131 --> 00:17:48,022
dan sekarang dia jadi anggota grup.

140
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:57,636
Eh, lo lihat
sang putri gak?

141
00:17:57,637 --> 00:17:59,374
Enggak tuh.

142
00:18:31,341 --> 00:18:32,341
Hei.

143
00:18:32,342 --> 00:18:34,541
Malah ngelewatin pesta sendiri.

144
00:18:36,038 --> 00:18:38,479
Gue benci ulang tahun.

145
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,282
Iya sih.

146
00:18:39,283 --> 00:18:41,977
Luigi pas ultah ke-10
nangis terus.

147
00:18:41,978 --> 00:18:45,156
Katanya masa kecilnya udah abis.

148
00:18:45,916 --> 00:18:50,359
Lucunya, hari ini tuh
bukan ultah beneran gue.

149
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:53,230
Cuma tanggal pas
para Toad nemuin gue.

150
00:18:53,231 --> 00:18:55,925
Mereka gak tahu
asal-usul gue dari mana.

151
00:18:54,926 --> 00:19:01,370
Seumur hidup gue selalu
penasaran keluarga gue di mana.

152
00:19:01,371 --> 00:19:03,834
Pasti berat banget ya.

153
00:19:03,835 --> 00:19:08,310
Kadang gue ngerasa hampa banget.

154
00:19:09,907 --> 00:19:13,250
Kira-kira karena ini bukan
ulang tahun asli lo,

155
00:19:13,251 --> 00:19:15,153
lo pasti gak mau kado kan.

156
00:19:15,154 --> 00:19:16,319
Mario!

157
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:19,453
Oke, oke. Fine.

158
00:19:22,359 --> 00:19:24,359
Oh.

159
00:19:28,596 --> 00:19:30,431
Suka banget.

160
00:19:35,339 --> 00:19:37,504
Hah?

161
00:19:40,377 --> 00:19:42,773
Wah.

162
00:19:55,755 --> 00:19:57,392
Lihat tuh.

163
00:20:11,870 --> 00:20:14,343
- Wih.
- Wah.

164
00:20:14,444 --> 00:20:16,906
Wah.

165
00:20:21,451 --> 00:20:23,583
Oh.

166
00:21:28,650 --> 00:21:33,291
Putri Peach, akhirnya
ketemu juga.

167
00:21:33,292 --> 00:21:34,391
Oh.

168
00:21:42,763 --> 00:21:45,126
Udah mendingan sekarang?

169
00:21:46,437 --> 00:21:48,537
Gak nyangka ini beneran kamu.

170
00:21:48,538 --> 00:21:52,970
Mama sering banget bacain dongeng
sebelum tidur tentang kamu.

171
00:21:52,971 --> 00:21:54,543
Tentang gue?

172
00:21:54,544 --> 00:21:55,478
Yakin?

173
00:21:55,479 --> 00:21:58,107
Kata Mama kalau terjadi sesuatu
sama dia,

174
00:21:58,108 --> 00:22:01,484
suruh cari kamu,
dan kamu bakal bantuin kita.

175
00:22:01,485 --> 00:22:04,520
Putri, mama kami diculik.

176
00:22:04,521 --> 00:22:05,356
Kejadiannya gimana?

177
00:22:05,357 --> 00:22:08,249
Ada robot raksasa yang bawa dia
ke planet menyeramkan

178
00:22:08,250 --> 00:22:10,955
di luar Galaksi Gateway.

179
00:22:10,956 --> 00:22:12,890
Bisa bantu kami?

180
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:19,293
Anu, Peach, sori, tadi aku sudah coba...

181
00:22:18,294 --> 00:22:19,701
Iya, iya, kami tadi nguping kok.

182
00:22:19,702 --> 00:22:21,406
Jangan pernah kepikiran
buat pergi ya.

183
00:22:21,407 --> 00:22:24,200
Teman-teman, bisa kasih
putri waktu sebentar?

184
00:22:24,201 --> 00:22:26,301
Dia pasti tahu harus gimana.

185
00:22:26,302 --> 00:22:27,973
Gue gak setuju, Mario.

186
00:22:27,974 --> 00:22:30,239
Meskipun piyama gue
bilang sebaliknya.

187
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:32,307
Gak ada yang perlu dipikirin lagi.

188
00:22:32,308 --> 00:22:33,682
Dia gak boleh pergi.

189
00:22:33,683 --> 00:22:34,914
Betul, betul, betul.

190
00:22:34,915 --> 00:22:36,311
Oke semuanya, ayo bubar.

191
00:22:36,312 --> 00:22:39,555
Kita bahas lagi
besok pagi ya.

192
00:22:41,954 --> 00:22:44,317
Selamat malam, Putri.

193
00:22:53,471 --> 00:22:55,802
Toad, kemasin barang kita.

194
00:23:27,604 --> 00:23:29,407
Wah!

195
00:23:34,336 --> 00:23:38,514
Woo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

196
00:23:43,653 --> 00:23:44,653
Ada apa nih?

197
00:23:43,654 --> 00:23:45,687
Dia ninggalin ini buat lo.

198
00:23:49,021 --> 00:23:50,285
<i>Halo, si Kumis,</i>

199
00:23:49,286 --> 00:23:52,057
<i>Gue pergi ke Galaksi Gateway
buat mulai nyari</i>

200
00:23:52,058 --> 00:23:53,322
<i>ibunya Luma.</i>

201
00:23:53,323 --> 00:23:56,468
<i>Gue titip Kerajaan
ke tangan lo ya.</i>

202
00:23:56,469 --> 00:23:59,932
<i>Salam hangat, Peach.</i>

203
00:24:01,803 --> 00:24:02,638
"Salam hangat."

204
00:24:01,639 --> 00:24:04,674
Ciye... itu pertanda bagus tuh.

205
00:24:04,675 --> 00:24:06,544
Putri Peach pergi?

206
00:24:06,545 --> 00:24:07,776
Duh, gawat!

207
00:24:13,045 --> 00:24:15,782
Semuanya, harap tenang.

208
00:24:16,180 --> 00:24:17,917
Super Mario Brothers

209
00:24:16,918 --> 00:24:19,381
bakal jagain Kerajaan ini.

210
00:25:12,269 --> 00:25:14,303
Ha!

211
00:25:27,889 --> 00:25:28,592
Woo-hoo!

212
00:26:04,321 --> 00:26:06,058
Terus gimana sekarang?

213
00:26:39,664 --> 00:26:41,863
Halo, raksasa.

214
00:26:41,864 --> 00:26:42,699
Aah! Oh.

215
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:43,668
Kaget gue.

216
00:26:43,669 --> 00:26:44,900
Lo mau ketemu kami?

217
00:26:44,901 --> 00:26:47,529
Jangan gerak. Gue ke sana sekarang.

218
00:26:50,840 --> 00:26:52,973
♪ Menyeruput sup ♪

219
00:26:51,974 --> 00:26:53,876
♪ Bersihin cat ♪

220
00:26:57,176 --> 00:27:00,750
♪ Dan juga rapiin
pohon bonsai. ♪

221
00:26:59,751 --> 00:27:02,048
Oke deh.

222
00:27:07,252 --> 00:27:10,319
Woi, Luigi!

223
00:27:10,728 --> 00:27:12,630
Ada apa, Mario?

224
00:27:13,830 --> 00:27:14,588
Lihat nih.

225
00:27:13,589 --> 00:27:17,295
Gue bikin karya agung
buat Putri Peach.

226
00:27:17,296 --> 00:27:19,561
Gimana menurut lo?

227
00:27:19,562 --> 00:27:21,672
Jujur ya.

228
00:27:23,598 --> 00:27:25,401
Suka sih sama warnanya.

229
00:27:24,402 --> 00:27:28,075
Tapi kritik gue cuma satu,
ini sampah.

230
00:27:28,076 --> 00:27:31,441
Berani-beraninya lo ngatain
karya agung gue kayak gitu!

231
00:27:31,442 --> 00:27:33,212
Lo pikir melukis itu gampang?

232
00:27:33,213 --> 00:27:37,149
Gue bakar sampai
tinggal tulang lo nanti!

233
00:27:38,547 --> 00:27:40,724
Waduh.

234
00:27:40,725 --> 00:27:41,692
Sori ya soal itu.

235
00:27:40,693 --> 00:27:42,957
Tadi itu sisi Bowser lama yang ngomong.

236
00:27:41,958 --> 00:27:47,489
Kayaknya gue masih berjuang
ngelawan sisi gelap gue deh.

237
00:27:47,490 --> 00:27:49,590
Santai aja.

238
00:27:49,591 --> 00:27:50,800
Udah baikan kok.

239
00:27:49,801 --> 00:27:52,770
Lagian, ini bukan sekadar kado.

240
00:27:52,771 --> 00:27:54,596
Ini tanda perdamaian.

241
00:27:54,597 --> 00:27:55,872
Gue pengen dia bebasin gue.

242
00:27:55,873 --> 00:27:59,843
Bukan karena gue berkelakuan baik,
tapi karena gue luar biasa!

243
00:28:00,844 --> 00:28:01,976
Dia gak bakal bebasin lo.

244
00:28:00,977 --> 00:28:03,473
Dan jangan pernah minta
buat dibalikin jadi gede lagi.

245
00:28:03,474 --> 00:28:06,245
Padahal gue
udah tobat total nih?

246
00:28:06,246 --> 00:28:07,686
Mario, dia beneran udah berubah.

247
00:28:07,687 --> 00:28:10,722
Kami bahkan ikut
klub buku bareng tiap minggu.

248
00:28:10,723 --> 00:28:11,789
Gue yang bawa supnya.

249
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:16,221
Dia gak percaya sama lo,
begitu juga gue.

250
00:28:17,454 --> 00:28:19,158
Oh, mending lo mulai percaya deh

251
00:28:18,159 --> 00:28:22,062
sebelum gue telan jiwa lo dan...

252
00:28:24,527 --> 00:28:26,396
Maaf, itu... cuma refleks...

253
00:28:26,397 --> 00:28:27,661
Wah, parah.

254
00:28:26,662 --> 00:28:30,533
Yaudahlah. Kalian tahu gak,
gue mau tidur dulu.

255
00:28:30,534 --> 00:28:31,633
Gue butuh tidur delapan jam

256
00:28:31,634 --> 00:28:34,944
biar gak beneran
berubah jadi monster.

257
00:28:35,945 --> 00:28:37,473
Aduh!

258
00:28:37,474 --> 00:28:38,606
Aduh, duh, duh, duh, duh!

259
00:28:40,312 --> 00:28:43,644
Kezentok! Kezentok!
Jempol gue kena ujung meja!

260
00:28:46,054 --> 00:28:48,616
Met bobo semua.

261
00:28:50,157 --> 00:28:51,729
Uh...

262
00:28:59,595 --> 00:29:01,870
Hah?

263
00:29:44,079 --> 00:29:46,047
Kita harus bawa
semua orang keluar.

264
00:29:45,048 --> 00:29:47,511
Ayo, ayo, ayo!

265
00:30:30,158 --> 00:30:33,192
Udah semua nih. Cabut yuk.

266
00:30:42,940 --> 00:30:45,039
Wah.

267
00:30:53,610 --> 00:30:57,282
<i>Mamma mia.</i>

268
00:30:58,120 --> 00:31:00,450
Wah.

269
00:31:22,441 --> 00:31:24,244
Atas nama para Koopa,

270
00:31:23,245 --> 00:31:27,016
gue tuntut kalian
bebasin bokap gue.

271
00:31:29,514 --> 00:31:32,021
Langkahi dulu mayat gue.

272
00:31:32,022 --> 00:31:34,583
Oke, siapa takut.

273
00:31:46,795 --> 00:31:50,171
Gimana kalau kita ulang lagi
dan kenalan dulu?

274
00:31:49,172 --> 00:31:52,471
Oke, anu, halo. Gue Luigi.

275
00:31:52,472 --> 00:31:54,143
Gue Bowser Jr.,

276
00:31:54,144 --> 00:31:57,872
dan sekarang
gue bakal bawa bokap gue.

277
00:32:21,731 --> 00:32:23,797
Wah.

278
00:32:36,251 --> 00:32:38,614
Ooh, ooh, ooh.

279
00:33:20,757 --> 00:33:22,560
Lo udah hebat banget,

280
00:33:21,561 --> 00:33:24,101
tapi kayaknya lo
butuh bantuan sedikit.

281
00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:31,040
Ah...

282
00:34:13,909 --> 00:34:14,909
Papah!

283
00:34:18,749 --> 00:34:20,320
Tunggu bentar!

284
00:35:20,712 --> 00:35:23,075
Semua aman kan?

285
00:35:25,222 --> 00:35:27,816
Kita di mana nih?

286
00:35:31,624 --> 00:35:32,723
Ha!

287
00:35:33,989 --> 00:35:35,792
Kebebasan yang manis!

288
00:35:34,793 --> 00:35:36,662
Lo bercanda ya.

289
00:35:36,663 --> 00:35:38,433
Dadah, pecundang.

290
00:35:38,434 --> 00:36:40,028
Woi, balik sini gak!

291
00:35:40,029 --> 00:35:43,064
Gak bisa. Lo gak bisa nangkep angin.

292
00:35:48,575 --> 00:35:49,839
Tapi gue baru aja nangkep.

293
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,775
Itu cuma kiasan kali!

294
00:35:54,152 --> 00:35:56,285
Aduh! Aduh! Aduh!

295
00:35:55,286 --> 00:35:56,286
Hei.

296
00:35:59,619 --> 00:36:00,355
Aduh! Duh!

297
00:35:59,356 --> 00:36:01,522
Berhenti gak!

298
00:36:01,523 --> 00:36:03,117
Gak bakal!

299
00:36:07,990 --> 00:36:11,266
Mendingan lo
keluarin dia sekarang.

300
00:36:15,536 --> 00:36:16,338
Ooh.

301
00:36:15,339 --> 00:36:17,868
Tegang banget tadi.

302
00:36:17,869 --> 00:36:21,069
Duh, malu-maluin banget sih.

303
00:36:21,070 --> 00:36:24,413
Gue masih dalam proses
tobat pelan-pelan.

304
00:36:24,414 --> 00:36:25,381
Sori ya, kawan.

305
00:36:25,382 --> 00:36:27,845
Lo ngarep gue jabat tangan
sama kura-kura

306
00:36:27,846 --> 00:36:30,287
yang anaknya baru aja nyerang gue?

307
00:36:30,288 --> 00:36:33,146
Anak gue?

308
00:36:35,985 --> 00:36:38,657
Gue udah lama gak ketemu dia.

309
00:36:37,658 --> 00:36:41,694
Mario, gue emang bokap yang payah.

310
00:36:41,695 --> 00:36:43,531
Dia pasti benci banget sama gue.

311
00:36:43,532 --> 00:36:44,532
Benci lo?

312
00:36:44,533 --> 00:36:47,997
Anak lo nyoba penggal kepala gue
cuma buat bebasin lo tahu.

313
00:36:47,998 --> 00:36:49,867
Dia pengen ketemu lo.

314
00:36:49,868 --> 00:36:53,343
Dia cuma butuh bimbingan aja.

315
00:36:53,344 --> 00:36:54,212
Beneran?

316
00:36:54,213 --> 00:36:58,139
Lo pikir gue masih punya kesempatan
buat deket lagi sama anak gue?

317
00:36:58,140 --> 00:36:59,074
Tuh kan, Mario?

318
00:36:59,075 --> 00:37:02,385
Dia udah mulai berani
jujur sama perasaannya.

319
00:37:02,386 --> 00:37:03,650
Gue baper banget nih.

320
00:37:03,651 --> 00:37:05,014
Yaudah, ayo gerak lagi.

321
00:37:05,015 --> 00:37:09,523
Kita harus cari jalan keluar planet ini
dan nyusul Peach.

322
00:37:28,675 --> 00:37:31,247
Lihat! Itu dia!

323
00:37:49,223 --> 00:37:51,961
Wah.

324
00:37:51,962 --> 00:37:55,502
Ayo cepetan. Nanti kita telat.

325
00:37:55,768 --> 00:38:00,276
Gila... Galaksi Gateway.

326
00:38:05,613 --> 00:38:08,516
Selamat datang di Galaksi Gateway.

327
00:38:07,517 --> 00:38:10,354
Gerbang utama kalian menuju galaksi lain.

328
00:38:15,458 --> 00:38:16,722
Toad, mau ke mana lo?

329
00:38:15,723 --> 00:38:18,955
Pasti ini mahluk
yang kita cari.

330
00:38:38,239 --> 00:38:40,416
Jangan! Jangan!

331
00:38:44,278 --> 00:38:45,685
Putri?

332
00:38:44,686 --> 00:38:47,049
Lo gak apa-apa?

333
00:38:53,122 --> 00:38:55,024
Ukiki tersesat.

334
00:38:54,025 --> 00:38:57,929
Kalian lihat teman-teman Ukiki gak?

335
00:38:57,930 --> 00:38:58,732
Oh.

336
00:38:58,733 --> 00:39:00,932
Ada monyet kecil nyasar nih.

337
00:39:00,933 --> 00:39:03,638
Sini, biar gue bantu.

338
00:39:06,641 --> 00:39:10,237
Monyet itu baru aja manfaatin
keimutannya buat nyolong!

339
00:39:09,238 --> 00:39:10,205
Toad, tunggu!

340
00:39:10,206 --> 00:39:13,175
Semua koin dan Power-Up
kita ada di situ!

341
00:39:13,176 --> 00:39:16,210
Sama draf novel gue yang belum kelar!

342
00:39:17,982 --> 00:39:21,280
- Permisi ya.
- Maaf, numpang lewat. Sori.

343
00:39:22,283 --> 00:39:23,283
Kena lo.

344
00:39:31,402 --> 00:39:33,194
Gak bisa kabur lo sekarang.

345
00:39:39,135 --> 00:39:41,806
Monyetnya tembus tembok, woi!

346
00:40:10,133 --> 00:40:11,771
Tetap dekat ya.

347
00:40:33,156 --> 00:40:34,057
Woi, lo!

348
00:40:36,434 --> 00:36:37,731
Woi!

349
00:36:37,732 --> 00:40:39,963
Balikin tas gue!

350
00:40:51,009 --> 00:40:53,450
Pah, aku tahu Papah
ada di bawah sana.

351
00:40:55,211 --> 00:40:57,245
Tuan, percuma saja.

352
00:40:57,246 --> 00:41:00,182
Hal terpenting sekarang
di masa duka ini...

353
00:41:00,183 --> 00:41:04,626
...adalah saling menguatkan
satu sama lain.

354
00:41:04,627 --> 00:41:07,057
Bisa tenang dikit gak sih?

355
00:41:07,058 --> 00:41:09,532
Kita harus tetep nyari Papa.

356
00:41:15,297 --> 00:41:19,267
Jadi, anu, Bowser pengen ngomongin
sesuatu sama lo.

357
00:41:21,369 --> 00:41:22,303
Lo tahu gak, Mario,

358
00:41:22,304 --> 00:41:25,713
semua anak cowok percaya kalau
bokap mereka itu pahlawan besar.

359
00:41:25,714 --> 00:41:30,014
Gue gak mau ngecewain
anak gue karena badan gue cebol gini.

360
00:41:30,015 --> 00:41:32,115
Gue gak bakal bikin lo gede lagi.

361
00:41:31,116 --> 00:41:35,855
Lo mungkin biasa hidup
dengan ukuran segini,

362
00:41:34,856 --> 00:41:37,758
tapi gue terlahir buat jadi raksasa!

363
00:41:37,759 --> 00:41:39,628
Hilangin efek
Jamur Biru ini,

364
00:41:38,629 --> 00:41:43,566
dan gue bakal berjuang di sisi lo
sampai selamanya.

365
00:41:43,567 --> 00:41:45,095
Tawaran yang lumayan tuh.

366
00:41:45,096 --> 00:41:46,866
Selamanya itu lama banget lho.

367
00:41:46,867 --> 00:41:49,066
Kita gak bakal terkalahkan.

368
00:41:49,067 --> 00:41:50,331
Hmm.

369
00:41:50,332 --> 00:41:52,905
- Gak.
- Ayolah, pukul gue, Mario.

370
00:41:52,906 --> 00:41:53,675
Pukul!

371
00:41:53,676 --> 00:41:55,237
Iya, Mario, pukul aja. Kita-kita bisa percaya kok sama dia.

372
00:41:54,238 --> 00:41:58,339
- Pukul gue!
- Mario, udah hajar aja sekarang.

373
00:41:58,340 --> 00:41:59,307
- Ayo cepet.
- Ha!

374
00:41:59,308 --> 0:42:04,212
Pukul gue sekarang, dasar tukang ledeng
kecil yang gagal dan payah!

375
00:42:26,874 --> 00:42:29,677
Lo gak bakal nyesel deh.

376
00:42:31,846 --> 00:42:33,550
Aw.

377
00:42:33,551 --> 00:42:35,145
Kalian nungguin apa lagi sih?

378
00:42:35,146 --> 00:42:36,817
Ada istana di atas sana.

379
00:42:36,818 --> 00:42:38,885
Ayo. Ikutin gue.

380
00:42:42,725 --> 00:42:44,924
Woi!

381
00:42:51,228 --> 00:42:53,064
Sori.

382
00:42:53,065 --> 00:42:53,966
Wah!

383
00:43:01,007 --> 00:43:03,436
Wah.

384
00:43:31,004 --> 00:43:32,971
Putri.

385
00:43:47,691 --> 00:43:52,585
Ukiki,
lihat apa yang kamu bawa buat aku.

386
00:43:56,128 --> 00:44:00,867
Putri-putri itu nilainya mahal banget.

387
00:44:01,298 --> 00:44:04,036
Ukiki bilang novel kamu jelek!

388
00:44:04,037 --> 00:44:05,037
Aduh!

389
00:44:10,648 --> 00:44:11,472
Kenapa sih

390
00:44:11,473 --> 00:44:15,509
urusan kalian para putri itu
selalu aja diculik?

391
00:44:14,510 --> 00:44:18,885
Lo tahu sesuatu soal
putri yang hilang itu?

392
00:44:19,613 --> 00:44:21,218
Mmm.

393
00:44:21,219 --> 00:44:24,320
Gak tahu sama sekali.

394
00:44:24,321 --> 00:44:26,663
Dengerin ya, dasar bola lendir.

395
00:44:25,664 --> 00:44:30,898
Lo harus kasih tahu gue
persisnya di mana Rosalina.

396
00:44:29,899 --> 00:44:32,097
Emang lo mau apa?

397
00:45:04,493 --> 00:45:06,527
Oh, Tuan Putri.

398
00:45:05,528 --> 00:45:09,596
Lo bakalan nyesel udah gituin gue.

399
00:45:12,809 --> 00:45:15,711
Oh!

400
00:45:49,406 --> 00:45:51,242
Hiyat!

401
00:45:55,643 --> 00:45:56,984
Hiyat!

402
00:45:55,985 --> 00:45:58,249
Oh!

403
00:46:26,443 --> 00:46:28,916
Ooh, mantap!

404
00:46:54,405 --> 00:46:56,142
Dia di mana?

405
00:46:55,143 --> 00:46:59,342
Muka gue kayak tukang ngadu gak?

406
00:47:01,577 --> 00:47:03,380
Oh! Iya, kayaknya sih iya.

407
00:47:02,381 --> 00:47:04,151
Ini kesempatan terakhir lo.

408
00:47:04,152 --> 00:47:05,548
Oke, oke. Dengerin gue.

409
00:47:05,549 --> 00:47:09,320
- Anaknya Bowser yang bawa dia.
- Ke mana?

410
00:47:08,321 --> 00:47:11,783
Galaksi Space Junk.

411
00:47:16,328 --> 00:47:17,933
Toad.

412
00:47:16,934 --> 00:47:19,660
Siniin itu.

413
00:47:21,905 --> 00:47:26,204
Sambungin gue ke Bowser Jr. sekarang!

414
00:47:28,043 --> 00:47:31,539
Gerakin kaki bantet lo itu, manis.

415
00:47:33,884 --> 00:47:34,708
Halo.

416
00:47:33,709 --> 00:47:37,018
Kami butuh bantuan nih
buat keluar dari planet kalian.

417
00:47:36,019 --> 00:47:38,987
Kalian harus ngomong
langsung sama ratu.

418
00:47:37,988 --> 00:47:41,891
Tapi cowok muka serem itu
tetap di sini.

419
00:48:41,892 --> 00:48:43,222
Hmm.

420
00:48:42,223 --> 00:48:45,521
Biar gue yang urus.

421
00:48:50,659 --> 00:48:51,901
Halo, Yang Mulia.

422
00:48:50,902 --> 00:48:55,300
Kami lagi nyoba buat
pergi ke Galaksi Gatewa...

423
00:48:54,301 --> 00:49:00,074
Kalian alien yang udah ngerusak
ladang bunga gue ya.

424
00:48:59,075 --> 00:49:01,669
Penjarain mereka!

425
00:49:00,670 --> 00:49:04,176
Bawa mereka ke tambang madu!

426
00:49:05,707 --> 00:49:08,411
Gak bakalan selama ada gue.

427
00:49:10,987 --> 00:49:13,813
Seseorang harus tanggung jawab
atas kejahatan mereka.

428
00:49:12,814 --> 00:49:14,847
Lepasin mereka!

429
00:49:13,848 --> 00:49:17,223
Gue bakal gantiin hukuman mereka.

430
00:49:16,224 --> 00:49:19,995
Gue bisa ngerjain tugas
seratus orang cowok...

431
00:49:18,996 --> 00:49:22,030
...dan seenggaknya sepuluh ribu lebah.

432
00:49:21,031 --> 00:49:26,694
Tangkap gue aja dan kirim mereka
ke Galaksi Gateway.

433
00:49:32,668 --> 00:49:33,833
Hmm.

434
00:49:32,834 --> 00:49:35,076
Oke, sepakat.

435
00:49:34,077 --> 00:49:37,705
Bawa mereka ke Galaksi Gateway.

436
00:49:40,742 --> 00:49:43,083
Lo beneran mau begini?

437
00:49:44,383 --> 00:49:47,780
Ternyata lo gak sejahat
yang gue kira ya.

438
00:49:48,255 --> 00:49:50,025
Makasih ya.

439
00:49:49,026 --> 00:49:51,488
Simpen deh tuh.

440
00:49:53,590 --> 00:49:55,657
Jagain dia ya, oke?

441
00:49:54,658 --> 00:49:57,098
Pasti lah.

442
00:49:56,099 --> 00:50:02,432
Serangga malang ini
bakal nganter kalian.

443
00:49:07,703 --> 00:49:09,044
Berangkat!

444
00:49:08,045 --> 00:49:11,980
Bikin musuh lama lo bangga.

445
00:50:32,629 --> 00:50:36,236
Nanti kalau gue bebas, gue sama cewek gue
bakalan dansa...

446
00:50:35,237 --> 00:50:37,765
...sampai matahari terbit.

447
00:50:36,766 --> 00:50:39,976
Lo punya pacar di rumah?

448
00:50:41,209 --> 00:50:43,144
Dia ninggalin gue di pelaminan.

449
00:50:42,145 --> 00:50:45,212
Gue ditinggal gitu aja.

450
00:50:44,213 --> 00:50:46,983
Sekarang masih masa penyembuhan...

451
00:50:45,984 --> 00:50:50,513
...mencoba inget siapa gue
sebelum kenal dia.

452
00:50:50,614 --> 00:50:53,681
Jiwa yang sensitif banget ya.

453
00:50:57,489 --> 00:50:58,621
Hah?

454
00:50:57,622 --> 00:50:59,523
Tetep semangat ya!

455
00:50:58,524 --> 00:51:01,723
Lo pasti nemu yang pas suatu saat nanti!

456
00:51:03,363 --> 00:51:06,661
Ooh.

457
00:51:09,963 --> 00:51:12,107
Halo, Pah.

458
00:51:11,108 --> 00:51:13,339
Junior?

459
00:51:12,340 --> 00:51:16,638
Oh, anakku sayang!

460
00:51:17,740 --> 00:51:20,411
Kamu udah gede banget.

461
00:51:20,809 --> 00:51:23,381
Ini semua punya kamu?

462
00:51:23,647 --> 00:51:26,814
Eh, bukannya kamu harusnya
ada di asrama sekolah ya?

463
00:51:25,815 --> 00:51:27,782
Asrama sekolah?

464
00:51:26,783 --> 00:51:29,256
Lebih kayak asrama yang ngebosenin.

465
00:51:28,257 --> 00:51:30,422
Aku dikeluarin.

466
00:51:31,325 --> 00:51:34,459
Kamu beneran tumbuh gede
pas Papah gak perhatiin.

467
00:51:33,460 --> 00:51:36,098
Pah, kita bentar lagi bakal jadi

468
00:51:35,099 --> 00:51:40,135
dua orang paling berkuasa
di alam semesta ini.

469
00:51:40,136 --> 00:51:41,565
Inget gak pas
aku masih bayi kura-kura?

470
00:51:40,566 --> 00:51:45,404
Papah kerja keras banget
buat naklukin dunia.

471
00:51:44,405 --> 00:51:47,076
Tapi sesekali, pas Papah libur,

472
00:51:46,077 --> 00:51:51,113
Papah selimutin aku dan ceritain
dongeng sebelum tidur favorit kita.

473
00:51:50,114 --> 00:51:54,643
Itu adalah malam-malam
terindah dalam hidupku.

474
00:51:54,810 --> 00:51:56,382
Ceritain dongengnya lagi.

475
00:51:55,383 --> 00:51:57,779
Lagi?

476
00:51:12,135 --> 00:51:13,927
Dulu kala di zaman kuno,

477
00:51:12,928 --> 00:51:17,634
ada penjahat kuat
dengan rambut yang keren banget.

478
00:51:16,635 --> 00:51:20,208
Dia hobi banget naklukin segalanya.

479
00:51:23,036 --> 00:51:26,939
Nah, penjahat ini punya seorang anak.

480
00:51:27,612 --> 00:51:28,777
Mereka berdua keliling semesta

481
00:51:27,778 --> 00:51:30,713
berusaha nyari tempat
buat dijadiin rumah,

482
00:51:29,714 --> 00:51:35,520
tapi setiap tempat yang didatangi
itu payah banget.

483
00:51:34,521 --> 00:51:36,323
Najis!

484
00:51:35,324 --> 00:51:39,492
Jadi mereka mutusin
buat bikin planet sendiri.

485
00:51:38,492 --> 00:51:42,329
Lihatlah Planet Bowser,

486
00:51:41,330 --> 00:51:43,660
sebuah tempat suci yang jahat

487
00:51:42,661 --> 00:51:46,234
di mana mereka bisa habisin
sisa umur mereka.

488
00:51:45,235 --> 00:51:49,028
Mereka bangun
roller coaster jahat,

489
00:51:48,029 --> 00:51:50,304
jurang penuh lahar.

490
00:51:49,305 --> 00:51:54,803
Dan mereka ukir gunung raksasa
jadi bentuk kepala mereka.

491
00:51:53,804 --> 00:51:56,937
Dan di puncak planetnya,

492
00:51:55,938 --> 00:51:59,247
mereka bangun
meriam terbesar yang pernah ada.

493
00:51:58,248 --> 00:52:03,118
Itu bisa hancurin alam semesta!

494
00:52:03,285 --> 00:52:04,516
Mereka menamakannya...

495
00:52:03,517 --> 00:52:06,288
Senjata Boomsday!

496
00:52:05,288 --> 00:52:07,981
Buat tenaganya, mereka butuh...

497
00:52:06,982 --> 00:52:11,193
Putri terkuat
di alam semesta!

498
00:52:10,194 --> 00:52:13,624
Dan pas mereka udah serap
semua kekuatannya...

499
00:52:12,625 --> 00:52:17,595
...dan senjatanya siap, mereka keliling planet demi planet,

500
00:52:16,596 --> 00:52:21,566
ngehancurin semua orang
yang berani gak hormat sama mereka.

501
00:52:20,567 --> 00:52:22,336
Duarr!

502
00:52:21,337 --> 00:52:24,899
- Duarr!
- Duarr!

503
00:52:23,900 --> 00:52:28,144
Sampai mereka dansa
di atas abu alam semesta...

504
00:52:27,145 --> 00:52:30,509
...dan berkuasa jadi yang tertinggi!

505
00:52:29,510 --> 00:52:33,039
Selesai.

506
00:52:32,040 --> 00:52:35,679
Pah, besok malam ceritain lagi ya?

507
00:52:34,680 --> 00:52:36,977
Pasti dong.

508
00:52:35,978 --> 00:52:38,550
Met bobo, anakku sayang.

509
00:52:37,551 --> 00:52:40,320
Mwah.

510
00:52:43,556 --> 00:52:44,919
Ssst.

511
00:52:43,920 --> 00:52:48,329
Pah, aku udah bangunin planet itu buat kita.

512
00:52:47,330 --> 00:52:49,496
Beneran?

513
00:52:48,496 --> 00:52:51,365
Kita otw ke sana sekarang juga.

514
00:52:50,366 --> 00:52:52,564
Cuma Papah sama aku.

515
00:52:51,565 --> 00:52:55,665
Duo Bowser, gak ada tandingan.

516
00:52:59,066 --> 00:53:01,639
Tuanku sekalian.

517
00:53:00,640 --> 00:53:05,136
Kita punya masalah.

518
00:53:20,296 --> 00:53:22,858
Selamat datang di
stan informasi.

519
00:53:21,859 --> 00:53:24,266
Nama gue R.O.B.

520
00:53:23,267 --> 00:53:26,598
Lo butuh info apa nih?

521
00:53:25,599 --> 00:53:28,534
Kami harus cari pilot, buruan.

522
00:53:27,535 --> 00:53:32,131
Bisa banget. Pilot bisa ditemuin
di dek penerbangan,

523
00:53:31,132 --> 00:53:38,510
yang lokasinya ada di sebelah...

524
00:53:39,007 --> 00:53:41,976
sebelah...

525
00:53:40,977 --> 00:53:44,749
Aduh, R.O.B., lo bikin gue kesel aja!

526
00:53:43,749 --> 00:53:45,947
Maaf ya.

527
00:53:44,948 --> 00:53:47,982
Gue gak ada niat buat bikin kesel kok.

528
00:53:46,983 --> 00:53:49,148
Ugh! Toad!

529
00:53:48,149 --> 00:53:50,589
- Nama gue R.O.B.
- Gue tahu!

530
00:53:49,590 --> 00:53:53,185
Sip. Makasih udah mampir
ke bagian informasi.

531
00:53:53,186 --> 00:53:55,429
Dek penerbangannya di mana?

532
00:53:55,430 --> 00:53:57,629
Pas di sebelah...

533
00:53:58,994 --> 00:54:00,929
sebelah... sini.

534
00:54:00,930 --> 00:54:03,569
- Makasih ya.
- Sama-sama.

535
00:54:12,777 --> 00:54:14,811
Whee!

536
00:54:55,622 --> 00:54:56,655
Halo.

537
00:54:56,656 --> 00:54:59,559
Bisa anter kami ke
Galaksi Space Junk gak?

538
00:54:59,560 --> 00:55:01,495
Uh, ogah.

539
00:55:02,596 --> 00:55:03,398
Permisi.

540
00:55:02,399 --> 00:55:05,400
Berapa ongkosnya kalau anter kami
ke Galaksi Space Junk?

541
00:55:05,401 --> 00:55:07,567
Ketinggian buat pilot
kecil kayak gue.

542
00:55:07,568 --> 00:55:10,163
Gini deh, kasih tahu gue.

543
00:55:10,164 --> 00:55:11,505
Kenapa seorang putri

544
00:55:11,506 --> 00:55:14,772
pengen pergi ke tempat
paling bahaya di galaksi ini?

545
00:55:14,773 --> 00:55:16,444
Lo siapa sih?

546
00:55:16,445 --> 00:55:18,545
Jangan nanya yang pribadi-pribadi deh.

547
00:55:18,546 --> 00:55:21,042
Oh, sori-sori. Gue gak maksud...

548
00:55:21,043 --> 00:55:22,978
Gue Fox McCloud!

549
00:55:23,914 --> 00:55:28,115
<i>Ketua dari tim legendaris
Star Fox!</i>

550
00:55:28,116 --> 00:55:30,018
<i>Gue cuma peduli tiga hal:</i>

551
00:53:30,019 --> 00:55:31,591
<i>jagain Sistem Lylat,</i>

552
00:55:31,592 --> 00:55:32,691
<i>tempur bareng temen-temen gue,</i>

553
00:55:31,692 --> 00:55:37,630
<i>dan ngelakuin atraksi udara
yang super bahaya!</i>

554
00:55:37,631 --> 00:55:38,631
<i>Gaspol!</i>

555
00:55:38,632 --> 00:55:40,831
<i>Terus suatu hari,
mesin warp gue meledak,</i>

556
00:55:40,832 --> 00:55:42,965
<i>bikin lubang gede di
ruang dan waktu,</i>

557
00:55:41,966 --> 00:55:45,099
<i>dan gue tersedot masuk
ke alam semesta yang beda.</i>

558
00:55:45,100 --> 00:55:48,443
<i>Itu lah akibatnya kalau percayain
kodok jadi montir gue.</i>

559
00:55:49,104 --> 00:55:50,412
<i>Sekarang gue keliling galaksi lo,</i>

560
00:55:50,413 --> 00:55:52,007
<i>buat cari jalan pulang,</i>

561
00:55:52,008 --> 00:55:55,779
<i>jadi orang baik
kalau bayarannya cocok.</i>

562
00:55:56,210 --> 00:55:58,815
Oh, gue juga punya
sepatu luar angkasa yang keren.

563
00:55:58,916 --> 00:56:00,048
Wuih.

564
00:56:00,049 --> 00:56:02,215
Nah, itu tadi cerita latar
belakang cowok

565
00:56:01,216 --> 00:56:04,987
yang bakal anter kita
ke Galaksi Space Junk.

566
00:56:04,988 --> 00:56:08,826
Lo pikir gue lagi butuh duit banget
sampai mau dengerin itu?

567
00:56:11,995 --> 00:56:13,292
Oke deh, sepakat.

568
00:56:13,293 --> 00:56:14,535
Gue isi bensin Arwing dulu.

569
00:56:14,536 --> 00:56:17,196
Kita berangkat lima menit lagi.

570
00:56:19,673 --> 00:56:25,073
Tadi itu cowok paling keren
yang pernah gue lihat.

571
00:57:30,387 --> 00:56:33,081
Mario, gue punya ide cemerlang.

572
00:56:33,082 --> 00:56:34,148
Pas lo ketemu Peach,

573
00:56:34,149 --> 00:56:37,151
lo harus basa-basi dulu,
"Blah, blah, blah.

574
00:56:37,152 --> 00:56:38,823
Eh, halo. Apa kabar?"

575
00:56:38,824 --> 00:56:39,824
Terus, boom!

576
00:56:39,825 --> 00:56:42,860
Lo langsung ajak dia
jalan atau kencan.

577
00:56:42,861 --> 00:56:43,960
Gak tahu ya, Lu.

578
00:56:43,961 --> 00:56:47,502
Emang putri mau
kencan sama tukang ledeng?

579
00:56:48,768 --> 00:56:49,834
Mario.

580
00:56:49,835 --> 00:56:52,474
Dia bakal jadi putri paling beruntung
di seluruh dunia

581
00:56:52,475 --> 00:56:55,235
- kalau jadi pacar lo.
- He-eh.

582
00:56:55,236 --> 00:56:56,368
Dia pasti bilang mau,

583
00:56:56,369 --> 00:57:00,680
terus lo tanyain deh,
apa dia punya temen buat gue.

584
00:57:01,550 --> 00:57:05,212
Sekarang tinggal cari dia aja.

585
00:57:05,213 --> 00:57:09,051
Dia ada di sebelah...

586
00:57:09,052 --> 00:57:11,922
sebelah...

587
00:57:11,923 --> 00:57:14,562
Peach!

588
00:57:14,563 --> 00:57:16,157
Peach!

589
00:57:16,158 --> 00:57:17,290
Mario?

590
00:57:19,865 --> 00:57:22,295
Oh. Ada Yoshi juga.

591
00:57:22,296 --> 00:57:23,065
Yeay.

592
00:57:23,066 --> 00:57:26,265
Mario!

593
00:57:26,839 --> 00:57:27,674
Jabat tangan nih?

594
00:57:27,675 --> 00:57:29,071
Kirain bakal keren aja.

595
00:57:29,072 --> 00:57:31,480
Maksud gue,
ya biar kelihatan mantap aja.

596
00:57:31,481 --> 00:57:34,373
Iya-iya, emang
mantap dan keren kok.

597
00:57:34,374 --> 00:57:36,617
Mario, gue udah tahu
Rosalina ada di mana.

598
00:57:36,618 --> 00:57:39,587
Dan cowok ini yang
bakal anter kita ke sana.

599
00:57:46,254 --> 00:57:47,661
Pesawatnya oke juga.

600
00:57:46,662 --> 00:57:49,959
Kumis lo juga oke.

601
00:57:50,533 --> 00:57:51,423
Ayo berangkat.

602
00:57:56,165 --> 00:57:58,099
Yahoo!

603
00:58:11,719 --> 00:58:13,918
Lo harus suka sama pilot nakal!

604
00:58:13,919 --> 00:58:15,656
Menurut gue dia gak nakal.

605
00:58:14,657 --> 00:58:18,120
Dia mirip banget sama
anjingnya Bu Castellano.

606
00:58:18,957 --> 00:58:21,453
Emang anjing Bu Castellano
bisa kayak gini?

607
00:58:21,454 --> 00:58:23,191
Wih!

608
00:58:23,192 --> 00:58:26,425
Woo-hoo-hoo!

609
00:58:26,426 --> 00:58:28,394
Woo-hoo!

610
00:58:28,395 --> 00:58:31,066
Gue suka nih sama orang ini.

611
00:58:44,917 --> 00:58:48,182
Mendingan kalian
pegangan yang kenceng.

612
00:58:51,891 --> 00:58:53,660
Oh!

613
00:58:54,696 --> 00:58:57,796
Woo-hoo!

614
00:59:24,385 --> 00:59:28,288
Mereka bakal tanggung jawab soal itu!

615
00:59:32,525 --> 00:59:34,229
Tunggu, Junior.

616
00:59:33,230 --> 00:59:35,868
Tadi gue sempet ngobrol sama mereka.

617
00:59:34,869 --> 00:59:37,100
Mereka emang cupu banget,

618
00:59:36,101 --> 00:59:39,641
tapi gue tetep ngerasa gak enak
kalau harus ngebunuh mereka.

619
00:59:39,642 --> 00:59:42,973
Ngomong apa sih lo? Gak dibunuh?

620
00:59:43,503 --> 00:59:44,844
Wah, aneh banget.

621
00:59:43,845 --> 00:59:47,847
Oke. Yang satu ini
buat Papah ya.

622
00:59:47,848 --> 00:59:50,443
Pas gue beres sama mereka,
mereka bakal nangis

623
00:59:49,444 --> 00:59:51,686
manggil emak masing-masing.

624
00:59:50,687 --> 00:59:53,787
Eh, emangnya mau lo apain?

625
01:00:02,093 --> 01:00:03,258
Bowser.

626
01:00:02,259 --> 01:00:05,292
Kita ditipu sama dia.

627
01:00:16,569 --> 01:00:19,438
Aduh, bayinya.

628
01:00:22,410 --> 01:00:24,114
Apa...

629
01:00:24,115 --> 01:00:27,083
Aduh!

630
01:00:29,384 --> 01:00:30,186
Jangan!

631
01:00:30,187 --> 01:00:32,023
Boom!

632
01:00:36,732 --> 01:00:38,392
Tenang aja, Pah.

633
01:00:37,393 --> 01:00:39,492
Besok jam segini,

634
01:00:38,493 --> 01:00:43,298
Papah bakal lupa sama
para bocah ber-wearpack itu.

635
01:00:42,299 --> 01:00:47,170
Seluruh alam semesta bakal jadi milik kita!

636
01:00:53,276 --> 01:00:57,377
- Wah!
- Pegangan!

637
01:01:10,359 --> 01:01:12,261
Sekarang gimana?

638
01:01:14,671 --> 01:01:16,298
Gak mempan.

639
01:01:15,299 --> 01:01:18,596
Toad, bayi-bayinya!

640
01:01:19,841 --> 01:01:22,468
Hah... biar gue urus.

641
01:01:26,606 --> 01:01:29,541
Sini kalian.

642
01:01:36,693 --> 01:01:38,759
Whoo!

643
01:01:42,831 --> 01:01:43,765
Hah?

644
01:01:57,274 --> 01:01:58,978
Yoshi!

645
01:01:58,979 --> 01:02:00,111
Balik sini!

646
01:01:59,112 --> 01:02:01,948
Yoshi. Yoshi.

647
01:02:00,949 --> 01:02:03,378
Yoshi!

648
01:02:13,356 --> 01:02:15,225
Sini dong!

649
01:02:14,226 --> 01:02:17,688
Whee.

650
01:02:18,966 --> 01:02:21,066
Luigi!

651
01:02:21,067 --> 01:02:22,595
Lo lagi ngapain sih?

652
01:02:21,596 --> 01:02:24,498
Berhenti!

653
01:02:31,880 --> 01:02:34,145
Mario!

654
01:02:47,687 --> 01:02:49,864
Ssst!

655
01:03:02,273 --> 01:03:03,009
Yoshi!

656
01:03:02,010 --> 01:03:05,880
Yoshi! Yoshi!

657
01:03:30,532 --> 01:03:32,939
Nih.

658
01:03:33,040 --> 01:03:34,810
Eh... Tunggu, bentar.

659
01:03:33,811 --> 01:03:36,471
Aduh, jangan. Lepasin!
Lepasin gak! Lepasin!

660
01:03:35,472 --> 01:03:38,275
Siniin! Siniin!
Siniin buat gue!

661
01:03:37,276 --> 01:03:40,881
Siniin... siniin pistolnya!

662
01:04:57,322 --> 01:04:58,685
Oh. Anu...

663
01:05:02,063 --> 01:05:04,097
Gue sempet suka sih jadi bayi.

664
01:05:03,098 --> 01:05:06,528
Semua pikiran serem yang lewat di kepala
langsung ilang gitu aja, lo tahu kan?

665
01:05:05,529 --> 01:05:09,036
Tenang, kita bakal benerin lo biar kayak baru lagi.

666
01:05:09,906 --> 01:05:11,599
Gak apa-apa kok, cuma lecet dikit.

667
01:05:10,600 --> 01:05:14,338
Tenang aja. Cuma penyok dikit kok.

668
01:05:13,339 --> 01:05:16,802
Cuma penyok doang.

669
01:05:26,054 --> 01:05:29,518
Denger ya. Kita pasti nemu jalan
keluar dari planet ini.

670
01:05:28,519 --> 01:05:31,554
Mario, kita jaraknya beda galaksi
dari Rosalina,

671
01:05:31,555 --> 01:05:33,127
kapal kita rusak parah,

672
01:05:33,128 --> 01:05:36,591
dan entah kenapa kita nambah
dinosaurus terus!

673
01:05:38,660 --> 01:05:40,100
Gue tahu lo lagi kesel.

674
01:05:39,101 --> 01:05:42,465
Putri itu gak boleh kesel tahu!

675
01:05:41,466 --> 01:05:47,074
Yaudah. Kalau gitu boleh gak
gue ikutan gak-kesel bareng lo?

676
01:05:55,017 --> 01:05:56,182
Tes, tes, dicoba.

677
01:05:55,183 --> 01:05:58,547
Di sini Hijau Gede bareng Merah Kecil
dan anjing pemburu.

678
01:05:57,548 --> 01:06:00,912
Kami lagi butuh evakuasi...

679
01:05:59,913 --> 01:06:01,990
Buruan ya.

680
01:06:00,991 --> 01:06:03,783
Habis tabrakan beruntun
di kota dinosaurus nih.

681
01:06:02,784 --> 01:06:05,818
Kami lagi bawa kargo kerajaan...

682
01:06:04,819 --> 01:06:07,820
seekor kadal guntur dan...

683
01:06:06,821 --> 01:06:09,888
- Ayo dong!
- Lo pasti bisa!

684
01:06:11,825 --> 01:06:14,233
Aduh!

685
01:06:17,468 --> 01:06:18,765
Woo-hoo!

686
01:06:20,042 --> 01:06:23,935
Lihat nih akibatnya kalau
kalian gak tidur tepat waktu.

687
01:06:22,936 --> 01:06:26,542
Mayday, Mayday.

688
01:06:25,543 --> 01:06:29,809
Ini Luigi si gukguk gede
laporan selesai. Ganti.

689
01:06:28,810 --> 01:06:32,580
Luigi?

690
01:06:40,227 --> 01:06:42,954
Kumis mereka emang aneh sih,

691
01:06:41,955 --> 01:06:45,792
tapi mereka bukan orang jahat.

692
01:06:44,793 --> 01:06:46,530
Mereka temen kamu, kan?

693
01:06:46,531 --> 01:06:49,005
Gak ada yang lebih bahaya
daripada seorang temen.

694
01:06:49,006 --> 01:06:54,537
Pas kamu lagi lengah,
mereka bakal nusuk dari belakang.

695
01:06:53,538 --> 01:06:54,736
Papah denger itu dari mana?

696
01:06:54,737 --> 01:06:58,244
Itu yang Papah bilang pas nganterin kamu

697
01:06:57,245 --> 01:07:00,642
di hari pertama sekolah.

698
01:06:59,643 --> 01:07:02,347
Gue emang bokap teladan.

699
01:07:01,348 --> 01:07:05,515
Temen-temen kamu itu
cuma mau ngerusak kamu,

700
01:07:04,516 --> 01:07:07,814
bikin kamu jadi orang lain.

701
01:07:06,815 --> 01:07:10,949
Kamu tahu siapa yang gak bakal nyakitin kamu?

702
01:07:09,950 --> 01:07:13,028
Keluarga kamu sendiri.

703
01:07:12,029 --> 01:07:15,228
Keluarga itu selamanya.

704
01:07:14,229 --> 01:07:18,065
Merem deh.

705
01:07:23,435 --> 01:07:24,435
Pah.

706
01:07:24,436 --> 01:07:26,767
Sabar dulu.

707
01:07:26,768 --> 01:07:29,110
Nah, buka sekarang.

708
01:07:45,655 --> 01:07:49,130
Teman-teman, ada sesuatu
yang aneh banget...

709
01:07:49,131 --> 01:07:51,395
...terbang ke arah kita.

710
01:07:58,272 --> 01:08:00,834
- Wih.
- Wah.

711
01:08:09,008 --> 01:08:11,614
Mario!

712
01:08:11,615 --> 01:08:13,615
Ayo berangkat!

713
01:08:30,238 --> 01:08:35,967
Kita bakal sampai di Galaksi Space Junk
sebelum jam tidur siang.

714
01:09:17,076 --> 01:09:18,417
<i>Zaman dahulu kala,</i>

715
01:09:18,418 --> 01:09:23,719
<i>ada putri pemberani dan baik hati
bernama Peach.</i>

716
01:09:26,492 --> 01:09:30,659
<i>Ceritanya dimulai
bertahun-tahun yang lalu...</i>

717
01:09:30,958 --> 01:09:33,432
<i>pas dia tinggal di sebuah planet kecil</i>

718
01:09:33,433 --> 01:09:35,830
<i>bersama saudaranya, Rosalina.</i>

719
01:09:35,831 --> 01:09:40,175
<i>Kedua putri ini
tercipta dari debu bintang.</i>

720
01:09:43,806 --> 01:09:49,107
<i>Cinta mereka bersinar seterang
bintang-bintang itu sendiri.</i>

721
01:09:50,142 --> 01:09:55,552
<i>Bersama, mereka bisa memanggil
kekuatan kosmos.</i>

722
01:10:07,665 --> 01:10:13,537
<i>Tapi kekuatan jahat menginginkan
kekuatan itu buat mereka sendiri.</i>

723
01:10:14,034 --> 01:10:21,105
<i>Rosalina harus mengirim Peach
pergi jauh demi keselamatannya.</i>

724
01:10:29,456 --> 01:10:31,655
Jangan! Jangan!

725
01:10:36,331 --> 01:10:39,465
<i>Para Toad membesarkan
dan melindunginya...</i>

726
01:10:39,466 --> 01:10:44,997
<i>sampai dia tumbuh cukup kuat
untuk melindungi mereka.</i>

727
01:11:01,114 --> 01:11:06,821
Pah, selamat datang di Planet Bowser!

728
01:11:24,940 --> 01:11:27,106
Kamu beneran bangun semua ini?

729
01:11:27,107 --> 01:11:28,173
Gak cuma itu aja.

730
01:11:28,174 --> 01:11:33,716
Kita punya Senjata Boomsday
milik kita sendiri!

731
01:11:35,555 --> 01:11:40,756
Dan putri yang aku culik
buat jadi tenaganya.

732
01:11:43,123 --> 01:11:46,631
Alam semesta gak bakal
pernah maafin lo.

733
01:11:46,632 --> 01:11:48,633
Emang ini takdir lo.

734
01:11:47,634 --> 01:11:50,063
Di sini lah tempat lo.

735
01:11:49,064 --> 01:11:53,770
Malam ini kita hancurkan
Kerajaan Jamur.

736
01:11:53,771 --> 01:11:57,168
Besok, seluruh alam semesta!

737
01:11:57,610 --> 01:12:02,812
Bowser! Bowser! Bowser! Bowser!

738
01:12:02,813 --> 01:12:06,387
Bowser! Bowser! Bowser!

739
01:12:06,388 --> 01:12:10,016
Yeay! Hidup sang raja!

740
01:12:10,359 --> 01:12:13,151
Mereka nungguin Papah tuh.

741
01:12:14,330 --> 01:12:18,223
Kadang, dalam hidup yang bagai
lintasan Rainbow Road ini...

742
01:12:17,224 --> 01:12:19,158
...kita bisa kehilangan arah.

743
01:18:159 --> 01:12:23,096
Tapi kalau lo beruntung, versi kecil
dari diri lo sendiri...

744
01:12:22,097 --> 01:12:27,133
...bakal bantu lo inget
apa panggilan hidup lo yang bener.

745
01:12:27,134 --> 01:12:29,905
Pasukan Koopa-ku...

746
01:12:29,906 --> 01:12:32,039
raja kalian sudah kembali!

747
01:13:38,810 --> 01:13:41,306
Kita bakal mendarat di planet itu.

748
01:13:40,307 --> 01:13:42,747
Pasang sabuk pengaman.

749
01:13:41,748 --> 01:13:45,782
Bakal jadi gila nih.

750
01:13:46,983 --> 01:13:50,248
Tim Star Fox sudah siap.

751
01:13:51,724 --> 01:13:53,252
Keren.

752
01:14:19,950 --> 01:14:21,214
Ayo kita hajar.

753
01:14:26,957 --> 01:14:29,628
Serangan datang!

754
01:14:32,633 --> 01:14:35,162
Lakuin manuver gulingan!

755
01:14:36,868 --> 01:14:38,704
Yeay!

756
01:14:48,913 --> 01:14:50,749
Giliaran lo, Kumis!

757
01:14:49,750 --> 01:14:52,915
Semoga beruntung.

758
01:14:56,723 --> 01:14:59,086
Wahoo!

759
01:15:16,006 --> 01:15:18,237
Wahoo!

760
01:15:35,960 --> 01:15:38,764
Gue gak ngerti itu maksudnya apa.

761
01:15:37,765 --> 01:15:41,965
Maksudnya lo lewat sini, kita lewat sana.

762
01:15:40,966 --> 01:15:43,636
Oh. Paham-paham.

763
01:16:25,647 --> 01:16:28,274
Oh.

764
01:16:34,183 --> 01:16:36,756
Ada penyusup! Ada penyusup!

765
01:16:35,757 --> 01:16:38,691
Tangkap mereka!

766
01:16:41,795 --> 01:16:43,455
Bentar lagi beres kok, Pah.

767
01:16:44,733 --> 01:16:45,732
Hah?!

768
01:16:45,733 --> 01:16:49,868
Tuanku, orang-orang rese itu balik lagi!

769
01:17:01,167 --> 01:17:02,530
Biar gue yang urus.

770
01:16:51,531 --> 01:16:57,270
Gue bangun sistem keamanan
level dewa nih.

771
01:16:59,813 --> 01:17:02,716
Mereka bakal hancur berkeping-keping.

772
01:17:04,213 --> 01:17:05,620
Gue suka banget jadi bokap.

773
01:17:04,621 --> 01:17:10,756
Rasanya baru kemarin dia bayi,
tahu-tahu udah gede aja.

774
01:17:30,712 --> 01:17:34,340
Halo, Peach dan Mario.

775
01:17:35,816 --> 01:17:39,577
Siap-siap ketemu ajal kalian.

776
01:18:39,077 --> 01:18:41,407
Wah!

777
01:18:49,318 --> 01:18:52,484
Kena kalian sekarang.

778
01:19:14,783 --> 01:19:16,607
Woo-hoo!

779
01:19:28,929 --> 01:19:32,964
Gak bakal gue biarin mereka ngerusak ini.

780
01:19:53,822 --> 01:19:55,053
Bowser.

781
01:19:56,583 --> 01:19:58,353
Gak harusnya berakhir kayak gini.

782
01:19:57,354 --> 01:20:01,620
Gue tahu masih ada sisi baik di diri lo.

783
01:20:08,661 --> 01:20:11,036
Biarin kita lewat. Sekarang.

784
01:20:11,037 --> 01:20:11,872
Kalau enggak?

785
01:20:10,873 --> 01:20:13,566
Lo mau permaluin gue lagi di nikahan gue?

786
01:20:12,567 --> 01:20:17,471
Mau bikin gue jadi cebol lagi
terus dimasukin toples?

787
01:20:16,472 --> 01:20:19,539
Atau maksa gue ikut klub buku lagi?!

788
01:20:18,540 --> 01:20:19,815
Masa-masa itu udah lewat, Mario,

789
01:20:19,816 --> 01:20:26,920
sekarang Bowser sudah kembali,
dan lo bakal rasain kemarahan gue!

790
01:20:47,942 --> 01:20:50,636
Jangan! Jangan! Jangaann...!

791
01:20:53,508 --> 01:20:55,113
Papah!

792
01:21:14,166 --> 01:21:16,694
Papah.

793
01:21:37,024 --> 01:21:39,421
Gue adalah penguasa tulang-belulang!

794
01:21:38,422 --> 01:21:42,127
Gue adalah raja tengkorak!

795
01:21:41,128 --> 01:21:44,492
Dan gue anaknya!

796
01:22:00,245 --> 01:22:01,607
Mario!

797
01:22:03,017 --> 01:22:04,248
Sana pergi.

798
01:22:03,249 --> 01:22:05,985
Selamatkan dia.

799
01:22:33,311 --> 01:22:34,872
Oh!

800
01:22:33,873 --> 01:22:36,445
Wah! Oh!

801
01:22:53,100 --> 01:22:55,100
Wah!

802
01:23:17,355 --> 01:23:19,124
Aduh!

803
01:23:20,292 --> 01:23:22,457
Yoshi.

804
01:23:26,628 --> 01:23:27,925
Aneh banget.

805
01:23:36,902 --> 01:23:39,045
Aduh!

806
01:23:42,776 --> 01:23:45,381
Wah!

807
01:23:59,397 --> 01:24:01,497
Wah!

808
01:24:34,465 --> 01:24:35,894
Selesaikan ini, Lu.

809
01:24:41,175 --> 01:24:42,274
Ha!

810
01:24:41,275 --> 01:24:43,539
- Lu!
- Apa?

811
01:24:42,540 --> 01:24:45,673
Lo kan tahu gue gak pernah bisa nggambar!

812
01:24:57,785 --> 01:24:59,048
Mantap!

813
01:24:59,754 --> 01:25:01,018
Tidaakk!

814
01:25:35,196 --> 01:25:36,790
Atas nama para Koopa...

815
01:25:41,400 --> 01:25:42,169
Junior!

816
01:25:41,170 --> 01:25:45,864
Papah! Tolongin aku!

817
01:25:49,870 --> 01:25:52,640
Junior!

818
01:26:24,410 --> 01:26:26,246
Papah!

819
01:26:25,247 --> 01:26:28,478
Oh, anakku sayang.

820
01:26:59,005 --> 01:27:01,379
Rosalina.

821
01:27:07,552 --> 01:27:10,487
Gue butuh lo buat nyoba.

822
01:28:02,574 --> 01:28:05,410
Gue tahu lo bakal dateng jemput gue.

823
01:28:07,645 --> 01:28:11,109
Heh! Nemu tulang paha Papah nih.

824
01:28:10,110 --> 01:28:12,385
Pinter, anakku.

825
01:28:11,386 --> 01:28:14,651
Ayo cari kaki Papah sekarang.

826
01:28:14,652 --> 01:28:17,456
Mario! Mario.

827
01:28:16,457 --> 01:28:19,524
Sini kenalan sama saudara gue.

828
01:28:18,525 --> 01:28:22,329
Gue seneng banget
kalian bisa ketemu lagi.

829
01:28:21,330 --> 01:28:24,628
Gue emang suka reuni keluarga gini.

830
01:28:23,629 --> 01:28:26,399
Halo!

831
01:28:38,511 --> 01:28:39,511
Mama?

832
01:28:38,512 --> 01:28:40,271
Oh, Mama.

833
01:28:40,272 --> 01:28:45,385
Oh. Anak-anakku sayang.

834
01:28:44,386 --> 01:28:47,453
Kami kangen banget sama Mama.

835
01:28:46,454 --> 01:28:48,652
Mama juga kangen kalian.

836
01:28:47,653 --> 01:28:52,183
Ma, boleh gak kita main
ke Kerajaan Jamur?

837
01:28:51,184 --> 01:28:53,789
Aku pengen lihat istananya.

838
01:28:52,790 --> 01:28:55,791
Iya, boleh kok.

839
01:29:03,228 --> 01:29:06,372
Mana istananya?

840
01:29:06,737 --> 01:29:08,133
Anu, soal istananya...

841
01:29:07,134 --> 01:29:10,168
Iya, istananya itu, hmmm...

842
01:29:09,169 --> 01:29:12,268
Udah almarhum.

843
01:29:13,172 --> 01:29:15,580
Maksud lo apa?

844
01:29:14,581 --> 01:29:16,614
Kalian tahu gak?

845
01:29:15,615 --> 01:29:19,782
Kita bakal bangun lagi
istana yang paling keren.

846
01:29:18,783 --> 01:29:22,047
Siapa yang mau bantuin?

847
01:29:25,987 --> 01:29:28,856
- Aku!
- Woo-hoo!

848
01:29:59,889 --> 01:30:01,692
Wahoo!

849
01:32:31,744 --> 01:32:33,041
Jadi, mau ke mana lagi lo abis ini?

850
01:32:32,042 --> 01:32:36,209
Putri luar angkasa yang baik itu
udah benerin mesin warp gue...

851
01:32:35,210 --> 01:32:38,915
...jadi gue mau pulang sekarang.

852
01:32:37,916 --> 01:32:40,444
Semoga beruntung sama mereka ya.

853
01:32:39,445 --> 01:32:43,820
Keluarga mereka bener-bener ribet.

854
01:32:52,160 --> 01:32:53,798
Jangan khawatir, Nak.

855
01:32:52,799 --> 01:32:55,602
Gak ada penjara yang bisa nahan kita.

856
01:32:54,603 --> 01:32:57,395
Kita bakal keluar dari sini bentar lagi.

857
01:33:05,877 --> 01:33:07,504
Halo, para kroco.

858
01:33:06,505 --> 01:33:09,308
Mau coba kabur ya?

859
01:33:10,376 --> 01:33:12,245
Sekarang kalian harus tunduk
sama aturan gue.

860
01:33:11,246 --> 01:33:13,851
Tetep deket sama Papah, Nak.

861
01:33:12,852 --> 01:33:14,951
Dia gak bakal bisa matahin semangat kita.

862
01:33:13,952 --> 01:33:17,657
Awalnya raga lo yang ancur,
terus tulang-tulang lo.

863
01:33:16,658 --> 01:33:21,595
Sampai akhirnya cuma sisa debu.

864
01:33:20,596 --> 01:33:23,993
Bisa diem gak sekarang!

865
01:33:22,994 --> 01:33:26,226
Kebenaran gak bakal bisa lo bungkam.

866
01:33:25,227 --> 01:33:27,668
Malah bakal makin kenceng suaranya.

867
01:33:26,668 --> 01:33:31,495
Kayak suara genderang kematian
yang makin deket!

868
01:33:33,201 --> 01:33:34,399
Bum, bum,

869
01:33:33,400 --> 01:33:38,468
- bum, bum.
- Gak!

870
01:37:46,421 --> 01:37:49,621
Aduh... sini, sini,
monyet kecil yang malang.

871
01:37:48,622 --> 01:37:51,689
Aduh.

872
01:37:59,533 --> 01:38:02,073
Waduh, makasih banyak ya...

873
01:38:01,074 --> 01:38:03,877
Yang Mulia.